Precaution
==========
DO NOT RUN TESTS IN PRODUCTION SYSTEM OR OTHER SYSTEM WHERE RIST OF LOSS OF DATA IS NOT ACCEPTABLE.

Requirements
============
1. pgTAP    (http://pgxn.org/dist/pgtap/)
2. pg_prove (http://search.cpan.org/~dwheeler/TAP-Parser-SourceHandler-pgTAP/bin/pg_prove)

How to run
=========
1. Replace the password("__replace__appropriate_encryption_key__")
   which is written in the testcase as appropriate password before running the test.
2. Simply run a below command
   $ pg_prove -r -U <username> -d <dbname> 